product_category_tree: Beauty & Personal Care >> Hair Care >> Hair Styling Tools >> Hair Dryers
description: Enjoy a great hairstyle every day with healthier hair using the SENCOR SHD 8270 VT Hair Dryer. It features a professional AC motor and is infused with Argan Oil and Keratin to protect and nourish your hair, leaving it silkier and smoother. With 3 temperature levels, including a low temperature option for extra gentle drying and hydrated hair, and 2 speeds for perfect airflow, this hair dryer ensures efficient and fast drying, reducing drying time by 33%. The cool shot function helps to fix your hairstyle in place. The true ionic function of this hair dryer releases millions of negative ions, resulting in silkier, shinier hair without crinkling. It also enables faster drying and reduces static electricity, making your hair easier to comb and preventing hair damage. Designed for convenience, the hair dryer has an ergonomically shaped handle suitable for both left and right-handers. The removable rear grill makes cleaning easier, and the heating spiral maintains a constant temperature to prevent hair damage. It also includes a hanging loop for easy storage and comes with accessories, including two slim concentrators for hair drying and shaping, and a volume diffuser. Other specifications include a 3-meter long power cord, a power input of 2400 W, and dimensions of 270 × 240 × 95 mm. The weight of the hair dryer is 990 g.
